<br />
Free People:<br />
The Hobbits Power each other, and Gandalf helps them with some neat effects, (Gathering Wind mainly).  He also heals them.<br />
<br />
Shadow: <br />
All these minions rely on possesions, which means either two things:<br />
1: Your opponent will risk playing alot of Possessions, hoping to outlast your minions (but because there are too many, they won&#39;t)<br />
<br />
or<br />
<br />
2: Your opponent will stop playing possessions, hoping to negate all of your minions (Which is why we have the simple, damage +1 effects of the other Uruk Hai.) </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
